      <title>[인간본성의 법칙] 리더의 권위란 무엇인가?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1321/posts/2020-07-07-%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%84%EB%B3%B8%EC%84%B1%EC%9D%98-%EB%B2%95%EC%B9%99-%EB%A6%AC%EB%8D%94%EC%9D%98-%EA%B6%8C%EC%9C%84%EB%9E%80-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
